    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>mayo</strong>, <strong>chopped chives </strong>and <strong>half </strong>your <strong>white wine vinegar </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) in a small bowl – this is your <strong>chive mayo</strong></p>",
