    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes have been cooking for 15 min, heat a large wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) over a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>patties</strong> and cook for 4 min on each side or until nicely browned</p>",
