      "instruction": "<p>Once browned, top the patties with the<strong> cheddar slices</strong> and cook, covered, for a further 3 min or until the cheese has melted and the patties are cooked through (no pink meat!)</p><p>Meanwhile, slice your<strong> ciabattas</strong> in half and put them in the oven for 3-4 min or until toasted</p>",
