    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>baked beans </strong>and <strong>BBQ sauce </strong>in a small heat-proof bowl</p><p>Cook the <strong>beans</strong> in the<strong> microwave</strong> for 1 min, then stir them and return them to the microwave for 1 min further, or until piping hot – these are your <strong>BBQ beans</strong></p><p>Spoon the <strong>BBQ beans </strong>on the base of each <strong>toasted ciabatta base</strong>, then top with a <strong>cheeseburger patty </strong>and a <strong>toasted ciabatta lid </strong>– these are your <strong>BBQ beans on toast beef burgers</strong></p>",
