    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>BBQ beans on toast beef burger </strong>with the<strong> crispy potatoes</strong>, <strong>lettuce quarters </strong>and <strong>chive mayo</strong> to the side</p><p>Dress the<strong> lettuce quarters</strong> with the <strong>remaining white wine vinegar</strong>, 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil</strong> and a good grind of <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
